**ChatGPT** is the one everyone's heard of. It's made by OpenAI and was the tool that kicked the whole consumer AI explosion off in late 2022. It's the most versatile — broad knowledge, the biggest ecosystem of plugins and integrations, the easiest to start with. If you've never used any of these tools and just want to dip your toe in, ChatGPT is the lowest-friction way to do it. Where it falls down a bit is on long, complex prompts — it occasionally loses track of instructions you gave it earlier in the conversation.

