### Page 1 — Section opener

### Honest Limitations and Risks

Most "AI for business" content has a problem. It's written by people who either want to sell you something or want to look smart on LinkedIn. Either way, the awkward bits get glossed over. Hallucinations get a sentence. Privacy concerns get a footnote. Ethics gets nothing.

This section covers the bits the others skip. By the end you'll know:

